page.title: 12Myself- a boy called James.
page.content: My name is James. I was born in Newcastle General Hospital in 1976. I have brown hair and blue eyes and take size 3 in a shoe. My Dad is called James, he is 38 years old and my Mam is called Jean and is 36 years old. I have aunties called June and Pat and an uncle called George. My Grandad is called Charles and my Grandma is called Peggy. My favourite food is fish and chips. My favourite clothing is a track suit. My favourite subject at school is P.E. and I like doing project work and Maths. I do not like History. I have two pet budgies called Sparky and Billy. Sparky is 11 and we found Billy in a garden so we do not know how old he is. My Dad drives a car called a Peugeot and I have a bike called a Raleigh Striker. My favourite pop group is called Wham.
